data.description: This home features 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, 1,539 square feet ,situated in an established neighborhood with convenient access to various amenities. Additionally, it offers RV parking and a secluded front/courtyard. Upon entering, you're greeted by a generously sized living room complete with a charming brick fireplace. Adjacent to the living room is the kitchen and dining area. You'll find vinyl wood plank flooring throughout the living, kitchen, dining and laundry rooms. The kitchen boasts wood cabinets, corian countertops, and a garden window that looks out to the backyard. This home features a shaded patio with ceiling fans and a pool perfect for parties and warm summer days. Call for your private showing to view this property today!
